                            <cell role="num">137,544,872</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Note.</hi>—The above total is said to have been
                            increased by $13,000,000 since January 1, 1889, making about
                            $150,000,000 at date September 18, 1889.</p>
